## Remarks  
  
> [!NOTE]
>  <span data-ttu-id="32af7-347">從.NET Framework 2.0 開始，我們建議您先建立<xref:System.Xml.XmlWriter>所使用的執行個體<xref:System.Xml.XmlWriter.Create%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>方法和<xref:System.Xml.XmlWriterSettings>類別，以充分利用新功能。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="32af7-347">Starting with the .NET Framework 2.0, we recommend that you create <xref:System.Xml.XmlWriter> instances by using the <xref:System.Xml.XmlWriter.Create%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> method and the <xref:System.Xml.XmlWriterSettings> class to take advantage of new functionality.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="32af7-348">例如，下列 Microsoft Visual C# 程式碼：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="32af7-348">For example, the following Microsoft Visual C# code:</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
writer.Formatting = Formatting.Indented;  
writer.WriteStartElement("root");  
 writer.WriteAttributeString("xmlns","x",null,"urn:abc");  
 writer.WriteStartElement("item");  
 writer.WriteStartAttribute("href",null);  
 writer.WriteString("#");  
 writer.WriteQualifiedName("test","urn:abc");  
 writer.WriteEndAttribute();  
 writer.WriteEndElement();  
 writer.WriteEndElement();  
 writer.Close();  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="32af7-349">會產生下列輸出：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="32af7-349">Generates the following output:</span></span>  
  
```xml  
<root xmlns:x="urn:abc">  
 <item href="#x:test"/>  
 </root>  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="32af7-350">如果`ns`產生對應至目前的預設命名空間，沒有前置詞。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="32af7-350">If `ns` maps to the current default namespace, no prefix is generated.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="32af7-351">當寫入屬性值，這個方法會產生前置詞如果`ns`找不到。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="32af7-351">When writing attribute values, this method generates a prefix if `ns` is not found.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="32af7-352">當寫入項目內容，它會擲回例外狀況如果`ns`找不到。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="32af7-352">When writing element content, it throws an exception if `ns` is not found.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="32af7-353">如果這個寫入器支援命名空間 (<xref:System.Xml.XmlTextWriter.Namespaces%2A>設`true`)，這個方法也會檢查名稱是否有效，根據 W3C Namespaces in XML 建議事項 (http://www.w3.org/TR/REC-xml-names)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="32af7-353">If this writer supports namespaces (<xref:System.Xml.XmlTextWriter.Namespaces%2A> is set to `true`), this method also checks that the name is valid according to the W3C Namespaces in XML recommendation (http://www.w3.org/TR/REC-xml-names).</span></span>  
  
   
  
